In [161]:
from tensorflow.keras.models import Sequential
from tensorflow.keras.layers import LSTM, Dense, Dropout
In [167]:
lu = [50, 60, 80, 120]
dr = [0.2, 0.3, 0.4, 0.5]
In [173]:
stock_model = Sequential()
In [175]:
#First LSTM layer
stock_model.add(LSTM(units=lu[0], activation='relu', return_sequences=True, input_shape=(x_train.shape[1], 1)))
stock_model.add(Dropout(dr[0]))

#Remaining LSTM layers
for u, d in zip(lu[1:], dr[1:]):
    stock_model.add(LSTM(units=u, activation='relu', return_sequences=True))
    stock_model.add(Dropout(d))

#Final LSTM layer
stock_model.add(LSTM(units=lu[-1], activation='relu'))
stock_model.add(Dropout(dr[-1]))

#Output layer
stock_model.add(Dense(units=1))
